{"tid":567892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那冬奧隊其中一項目被DQ","createTime":"2018-02-21T09:19:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T09:59:08.000Z","uid":51271,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ab09e458ea181184b0219e52d2c61446ee0f056b","tid":567892,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T09:19:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=993910&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D993910%26csid%3D261_341&d=Px4FN%2BDPswkdiCZyJZdSqdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=40cbc33a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=993910&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n冬奧速滑女子接力國際滑聯駁回中國上訴<br />\n21.02.2018 16:30<br />\n<br />\n平昌冬奧昨晚舉行的短道速滑女子三千米接力決賽，中國隊以第二名衝線，但被判犯規，與獎牌無緣，中國隊提出上訴；國際滑聯維持裁判的判決，指中國隊沒有在比賽結束後三十分鐘內提出申訴，並公布判罰依據的圖片，表示不會再作任何評論。圖片顯示，中國隊最後一棒交接時，范可新驟然從外道變道，切至內線，阻擋正在滑行的南韓選手。<br />\n<br />\n中國隊主教練李琰昨晚就裁判判罰的一致性的問題，提出申訴，當時她曾表示，裁判仍在開會，因此申訴材料一時未能遞交上去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf68c5554f9eccb25f632f3e5030bfd05f671b9a","tid":567892,"uid":37661,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T09:20:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/vcpyRuwkg_6ZTrR5NtaW9w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/news_photo_A02b_nec01p04050713copy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail